      "seed": 314363340,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1633076448,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Session bootstrap  (once per chat session):\n  1.  agentfarm queries papi for MCP servers registered in this workspace\n  2.  agentfarm fires N parallel SLX runs with op=list_tools\n      each SLX HTTP GETs its MCP server's tools/list, returns schemas\n      agentfarm injects the aggregated tools list into the chat session context\n      (LLM sees them in the system prompt / leading message, not as ADK tools)\n\nPer tool invocation:\n  2.  LLM emits a tool intent  (via free-text or one generic call_mcp_tool callable)\n      agentfarm invokes the corresponding SLX with op=call_tool, {tool_name, args}\n  3.  SLX HTTP POSTs to its MCP server's tools/call, returns the result\n      result is appended to chat context for the LLM\n\nDrift handling:  on tool-not-found / schema-mismatch, agentfarm re-runs list_tools\n                 for that server, refreshes context, retries once.  No cron, no cache.\n\nTrade-off:  Two surfaces for the LLM  (existing task-search + tools-in-context).",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Session bootstrap  (once per chat session):\n  1.  agentfarm queries papi for MCP servers registered in this workspace\n  2.  agentfarm fires N parallel SLX runs with op=list_tools\n      each SLX HTTP GETs its MCP server's tools/list, returns schemas\n      agentfarm injects the aggregated tools list into the chat session context\n      (LLM sees them in the system prompt / leading message, not as ADK tools)\n\nPer tool invocation:\n  2.  LLM emits a tool intent  (via free-text or one generic call_mcp_tool callable)\n      agentfarm invokes the corresponding SLX with op=call_tool, {tool_name, args}\n  3.  SLX HTTP POSTs to its MCP server's tools/call, returns the result\n      result is appended to chat context for the LLM\n\nDrift handling:  on tool-not-found / schema-mismatch, agentfarm re-runs list_tools\n                 for that server, refreshes context, retries once.  No cron, no cache.\n\nTrade-off:  Two surfaces for the LLM  (existing task-search + tools-in-context).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
